genes.content: We present **Tongyi DeepResearch**, an agentic large language model featuring 30.5 billion total parameters, with only 3.3 billion activated per token. Developed by Tongyi Lab, the model is specifically designed for **long-horizon, deep information-seeking** tasks. Tongyi DeepResearch demonstrates state-of-the-art performance across a range of agentic search benchmarks, including Humanity's Last Exam, BrowseComp, BrowseComp-ZH, WebWalkerQA,xbench-DeepSearch, FRAMES and SimpleQA. > Tongyi DeepResearch builds upon our previous work on the [WebAgent](./WebAgent/) project.
